## Purpose
Print CLI build/version metadata. Daemon comparisons are excluded (no daemon in br).

## CLI
```
br version
```

## JSON Output
```json
{ "version": "0.1.0", "build": "dev", "commit": "abcdef", "branch": "main" }
```
Commit/branch may be omitted if unknown.

## Human Output
- `br version <Version> (<Build>)`
- Optional: `(<branch>@<short-commit>)`

